She got out of HotRod and transformed into lioness mode.  She ran 
over and jumped infront of the Predacons. "You may be bigger, 
stronger, and have more fire power, but YOU WILL answer Spitfire's  
question. What business have you with the ARK?" She growled loudly 
and stood infront of the bounty hunters.
